data.description: **Seller is highly motivated and will contribute $9,500 towards Buyers closing costs! Welcome home to 668 Carya Ct! This beautiful single-story home is located in the highly desired neighborhood of Alexandria Pointe in the historic city of Deland. This lovely home features 3 bedrooms, an open flex room, 2 bathrooms, 9 Foot Ceilings, and a 3 Car Garage with 2 ft of extra depth. The kitchen features an island and 42-inch cabinets. In addition, the Seller had solar panels installed and a water softener system throughout the home. Solar Panels are paid off! LOW HOA! Schedule your showing today! All information deemed reliable but not guaranteed and should be independently verified.
